  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 38,
      "chapterTitle": "黄初四年（223）癸卯 三十二岁",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "23509167_38_8714-8789",
          "range": "8714-8789",
          "rangeStart": 8714,
          "rangeEnd": 8789,
          "markText": "余告之曰：其形也，翩若惊鸿，婉若游龙，荣曜秋菊，华茂春松。仿佛兮若轻云之蔽月，飘飖兮若流风之回雪。远而望之，皓若太阳升朝霞；迫而察之，灼若芙蕖出渌波。",
          "colorStyle": 2,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1742178243,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-03-17 10:24:03",
          "chapterUid": 38,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23509167&chapterUid=38&rangeStart=8714&rangeEnd=8789",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/74c328107166b8af74cc976?chapterUid=38&rangeStart=8714&rangeEnd=8789"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "chapterTitle": "建安十年（205）乙酉 十四岁",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "23509167_19_5433-5492",
          "range": "5433-5492",
          "rangeStart": 5433,
          "rangeEnd": 5492,
          "markText": "南皮之游，存者三人。烈祖龙飞，或将或侯，今惟吾子，栖迟下仕。从我游处，独不及门。缶罄罍耻，能无怀愧？路不云远，今复相闻",
          "colorStyle": 2,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1742178213,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-03-17 10:23:33",
          "chapterUid": 19,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23509167&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=5433&rangeEnd=5492",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/74c328107166b8af74cc976?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=5433&rangeEnd=5492"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23509167_6_6071-6095",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "6071-6095",
      "markText": "先出其妾，妾肥，不能得出，嵩逃于厕，与妾俱被害。",
      "totalCount": 52,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23509167&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=6071&rangeEnd=6095",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/74c328107166b8af74cc976?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=6071&rangeEnd=6095"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23509167_38_2787-2821",
      "chapterUid": 38,
      "range": "2787-2821",
      "markText": "愚谓此篇可疑之处，不在辞章“工拙浅深”，而在此情节设计，太过戏剧性。",
      "totalCount": 51,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23509167&chapterUid=38&rangeStart=2787&rangeEnd=2821",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/74c328107166b8af74cc976?chapterUid=38&rangeStart=2787&rangeEnd=2821"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23509167_6_14940-14953",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "14940-14953",
      "markText": "性沈静，美姿容，尤好著述。",
      "totalCount": 48,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23509167&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=14940&rangeEnd=14953",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/74c328107166b8af74cc976?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=14940&rangeEnd=14953"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23509167_19_5433-5492",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "5433-5492",
      "markText": "南皮之游，存者三人。烈祖龙飞，或将或侯，今惟吾子，栖迟下仕。从我游处，独不及门。缶罄罍耻，能无怀愧？路不云远，今复相闻",
      "totalCount": 45,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23509167&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=5433&rangeEnd=5492",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/74c328107166b8af74cc976?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=5433&rangeEnd=5492"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23509167_24_13711-13763",
      "chapterUid": 24,
      "range": "13711-13763",
      "markText": "“兄弟”云云，当包括曹植在内。今存曹丕文字中，从未直接言及曹植。此是曹丕诗文中最接近说出曹植其人之文字。",
      "totalCount": 45,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23509167&chapterUid=24&rangeStart=13711&rangeEnd=13763",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/74c328107166b8af74cc976?chapterUid=24&rangeStart=13711&rangeEnd=13763"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23509167_26_3467-3514",
      "chapterUid": 26,
      "range": "3467-3514",
      "markText": "兄弟争嫡，史上常见，所涉权力继承及利益得失，本无所谓是非；但态度不同，风格有异，见出人品高下。",
      "totalCount": 45,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23509167&chapterUid=26&rangeStart=3467&rangeEnd=3514",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/74c328107166b8af74cc976?chapterUid=26&rangeStart=3467&rangeEnd=3514"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23509167_6_9114-9132",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "9114-9132",
      "markText": "然而《武文世王公传》不载，不知何故。",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23509167&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=9114&rangeEnd=9132",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/74c328107166b8af74cc976?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=9114&rangeEnd=9132"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23509167_25_18569-18630",
      "chapterUid": 25,
      "range": "18569-18630",
      "markText": "昔赤壁之役，遭离疫气，烧船自还，以避恶地，非周瑜水军所能抑挫也。江陵之守，物尽谷殚，无所复据，徙民还师，又非瑜之所能败也。",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23509167&chapterUid=25&rangeStart=18569&rangeEnd=18630",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/74c328107166b8af74cc976?chapterUid=25&rangeStart=18569&rangeEnd=18630"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23509167_29_7588-7646",
      "chapterUid": 29,
      "range": "7588-7646",
      "markText": "然而想当年路粹承曹操风旨，撰文罗织孔融罪名，置人于死地，亦未免深刻寡义，有背人之常情，日后自身下场，岂非现世报应乎？",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23509167&chapterUid=29&rangeStart=7588&rangeEnd=7646",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/74c328107166b8af74cc976?chapterUid=29&rangeStart=7588&rangeEnd=7646"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23509167_41_442-451",
      "chapterUid": 41,
      "range": "442-451",
      "markText": "夏五月，曹丕病故。",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23509167&chapterUid=41&rangeStart=442&rangeEnd=451",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/74c328107166b8af74cc976?chapterUid=41&rangeStart=442&rangeEnd=451"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23509167_43_1240-1254",
      "chapterUid": 43,
      "range": "1240-1254",
      "markText": "此序云“黄初八年”，当有错谬",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23509167&chapterUid=43&rangeStart=1240&rangeEnd=1254",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/74c328107166b8af74cc976?chapterUid=43&rangeStart=1240&rangeEnd=1254"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23509167_6_6182-6230",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "6182-6230",
      "markText": "陶谦遣都尉张闿，将骑二百卫送。闿于泰山华、费间杀嵩，取财物，因奔淮南。太祖归咎于陶谦，故伐之。”",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23509167&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=6182&rangeEnd=6230",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/74c328107166b8af74cc976?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=6182&rangeEnd=6230"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23509167_31_2051-2076",
      "chapterUid": 31,
      "range": "2051-2076",
      "markText": "自临淄侯植私出，开司马门至金门，令吾异目视此儿矣！",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23509167&chapterUid=31&rangeStart=2051&rangeEnd=2076",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/74c328107166b8af74cc976?chapterUid=31&rangeStart=2051&rangeEnd=2076"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23509167_41_5076-5087",
      "chapterUid": 41,
      "range": "5076-5087",
      "markText": "敢于就军国之事发表意见",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23509167&chapterUid=41&rangeStart=5076&rangeEnd=5087",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/74c328107166b8af74cc976?chapterUid=41&rangeStart=5076&rangeEnd=5087"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23509167_6_13271-13335",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "13271-13335",
      "markText": "允曰：‘昔武帝不杀司马迁，使作谤书，流于后世。方今国祚中衰，神器不固，不可令佞臣执笔在幼主左右，既无益圣德，复使吾党蒙其讪议。’",
      "totalCount": 33,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23509167&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=13271&rangeEnd=13335",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/74c328107166b8af74cc976?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=13271&rangeEnd=13335"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23509167_10_9913-9940",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "9913-9940",
      "markText": "方今天下大乱，智士劳心之时也。而顾观变蜀汉，不已久乎？",
      "totalCount": 32,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23509167&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=9913&rangeEnd=9940",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/74c328107166b8af74cc976?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=9913&rangeEnd=9940"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23509167_25_3532-3588",
      "chapterUid": 25,
      "range": "3532-3588",
      "markText": "念慈君之光惠，庶没命而不疑。欲力毕于旌麾，将何心而远之？愿我君之自爱，为皇朝而宝己。水重深而鱼悦，林修茂而鸟喜。",
      "totalCount": 32,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23509167&chapterUid=25&rangeStart=3532&rangeEnd=3588",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/74c328107166b8af74cc976?chapterUid=25&rangeStart=3532&rangeEnd=3588"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23509167_25_4136-4204",
      "chapterUid": 25,
      "range": "4136-4204",
      "markText": "尤其入黄初之后，曹丕对曹植严厉打击，略无亲情表示，态度冷淡；而曹植始终对曹丕怀有亲爱之情，态度热烈。双方日后表现，自建安中即可看出端倪。",
      "totalCount": 32,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23509167&chapterUid=25&rangeStart=4136&rangeEnd=4204",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/74c328107166b8af74cc976?chapterUid=25&rangeStart=4136&rangeEnd=4204"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23509167_38_21019-21030",
      "chapterUid": 38,
      "range": "21019-21030",
      "markText": "陛下临轩笑，左右咸欢康",
      "totalCount": 32,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23509167&chapterUid=38&rangeStart=21019&rangeEnd=21030",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/74c328107166b8af74cc976?chapterUid=38&rangeStart=21019&rangeEnd=21030"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23509167_7_736-776",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "736-776",
      "markText": "头白皓然，食不充粮。裹衣蹇裳，当还故乡。圣王愍念，悉用补郎。舍是布衣，被服玄黄。",
      "totalCount": 28,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23509167&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=736&rangeEnd=776",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/74c328107166b8af74cc976?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=736&rangeEnd=776"
    }
  ],
